data.description: New carpet and paint in this home with great views of the surrounding hills. Welcome to your cabin in the Rockies! Westcreek Lakes is a Sportsman's Paradise served by a private lake called Pine Lake that is full of Brown Trout and Rainbow Trout. It is one of the few private lakes that allows members to swim and recreate in and on the water. There are beaver dams and ponds throughout the area, and wildlife are everywhere. No need to trailer your OHV's, as you can ride from the property to the Rampart Range Trailhead. This property has plenty of recreational areas surrounding it: Gold Medal Waters for fishing, National Forest for Hunting, OHV trails, World Class Jeep Trails, World Famous Climbing at Turkey Rock and Sheep's Nose, Lost Creek Wilderness for horseback riding & Buffalo Creek for mountain biking all are within either riding distance or a 30 minute drive.
